Absa has launched a digital insurance product called Activate by Absa that includes motor vehicle, household contents, all-risk, and building cover. This product requires absolutely no paperwork, as any documentation and applications is done online, and this product is even available to those who are not Absa customers. You can get a quote and sign up for a policy in under 5 minutes – making this the obvious choice if you want great insurance without the fuss. Click here to sign up to Absa Activate and get a quote. “Consumer behaviour is changing and digitally enabled products and service offerings are increasingly important, particularly during social distancing measures,” said Absa Insurance executive Nirven Maharaj. “Absa wanted to create an end-to-end digital experience for customers, to help keep them and their families safer while insuring their assets,” he added. Absa therefore built the Activate product after conducting extensive international research and focusing on using technology and innovation to improve upon the traditional insurance model. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-499599 size-full" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1013165_Absa-Activate-banner-640x430pxDTP2.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1013165_Absa-Activate-banner-640x430pxDTP2.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1013165_Absa-Activate-banner-640x430pxDTP2-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The benefits of a digital insurance solution are endless, such as the ability to offer a variety of amazing value-adds and features. For example, Activate by Absa offers a telematics solution where your driving behaviours are tracked, monitored and rewarded. You will receive feedback on your driving habits through the Activate app, and depending on how well and safely you drive, you can earn up to 40% off your motor vehicle premiums back every month. Additional motor vehicle-related features include free emergency services, stolen vehicle recovery, and a panic button – all of which are focused on ensuring the safety of Activate customers. Another great benefit of Activate is that when you insure your contents and building with your vehicle your vehicle premiums are reduced– meaning the more you insure, the more you save. You will no longer need to fight with call centres over the best premium they can give you –Activate by Absa ensures you get the best value at all times. The lodging of claims has also been simplified, as you can instantly submit these on the Activate app with just a few taps. Getting a quote and policy from Activate by Absa takes under 5 minutes and is incredibly easy to do. There is therefore no reason to hesitate – get a quote today and simplify your insurance. Click here to sign up to Absa Activate and get a quote. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-499601 size-full" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1013165_Absa-Activate-banner-640x430pxDTP3.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1013165_Absa-Activate-banner-640x430pxDTP3.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1013165_Absa-Activate-banner-640x430pxDTP3-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />